9;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\">iFind蓝牙防丢器是什么<br/></h3><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">iFind是一款蓝牙防丢器，配合app，可以实现找到你放置iFind的位置，从而轻松找到你放置的物品位置，不再丢失物品。只要它离开手机一定距离，就可以app就会报警。它比一元硬币略大一点，和iPhone5s一样薄。<br/><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">装上电池后，无需任何操作，iFind就会自动开始工作。打开App后，iFind会自动连接手机，并通过蓝牙4.0发送数据到手机。电池可以持续工作两个月，更换也很容易。<br/><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">在手机上安装我们提供的配套app（即将在AppStore和GooglePlay上线），就能接收到iFind发来的位置数据，轻松找到物品功能。目前支持有蓝牙4.0的设备。<br/><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">当然，你也可以开发自己的app，iFind的信号发射和数据格式都遵循开放标准，只要参照蓝牙官方公开的文档，每个开发者都可以连接iFind，获取、分析数据。如果你想加入到智能硬件的浪潮中来，iFind是最好的入门开发工具。（对智能硬件创业有热情，有一定预算的开发者个人和团队，建议选择右侧的开发者套装回报→_→）。<br/><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">不光如此，iFind还可以是更多。如你所见，iFind像一个空白的icon。它属于我们，也属于你们。只要遵循蓝牙<a href=\"http://developer.bluetooth.org/gatt/Pages/default.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; text-decoration: none; outline: none; color: rgb(102, 153, 0);\">GATT</a>规范，每个开发者都可以参与探索iFind的功能。它可以越来越更聪明，它可以不只是温度计。我们不想定义它，你来。<br/><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">这是离你最近的智能防丢器。去年10月启动，目前量产方案已完成。<br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><h3 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 10px 0px 30px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\">关于我们</h3><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">qodome上海穹顶网络科技，专注于智能硬件领域。团队创始成员三人，在集成电路设计，软件开发等领域均有十年以上经验。<br/><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">我们希望为用户提供更好的服务，我们也希望通过我们的产品，为智能硬件开发生态圈的发展出一份力。<br/><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">联系邮箱contact@qodome.com<br/><br/></p><h3 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 10px 0px 30px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\">项目进度</h3><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">2013.10项目启动。<br/><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39