te-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">看那部纪录片的时候，片子里的人和在场观看的十几个人，眼泪都流到了一起。胸脯起伏，却憋着哭声，那种感觉，一辈子都会记得。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">那是一个有关“坚持”的故事，却又远超出人对这两个字的一般想象。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">如果说，做了三年《文周》后，我最大的变化是什么，我想其一便是，更爱哭了。对痛苦、忍耐、选择，变得更加敏感。哭，那是在什么办法都没有了，只剩一口气的时候，唯一可以做的事情。哭完，排掉心毒，能有重生的力气。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">总有人说，挺过明天，挺到后天，就好了。但今天，是要实实在在熬过去的。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">逼到头儿的时候，真想抽身出来，放一个长假，看看海，走村落，赚俩月的工资去我向往已久的佛罗伦萨……但天一亮，一开电脑一看稿子，什么就都忘了。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">走到今天，放弃和前进，同样艰难。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">而且是谁说来着，“失败不是悲剧，放弃才是。”</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">梦想不该是苦的，也不是“坚持”出来的。狠狠握着拳头咬牙说出来的不一定值得被尊重。借用一位读者的话，“任何持久的动力都来自积蓄够深的欲望。”&nbsp;欲望是一种本能。你不知道你要什么，你只知道你不能失去什么。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">做一个走在时代后面的人，需要多大的勇气和耐心？</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">当“文艺”染尽了坏名声，当传统媒体在衰退，当碎片式的新闻占据了人们日子里的边角余料，当“审丑”成了人民群众喜闻乐见的大众话题，我们却两手空空得要把一个贴着“文艺”两个大字、提倡深度阅读和精神享乐的杂志做起来。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">天方夜谭吧？</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">一个半点传媒知识没学过，几乎不看杂志的人，做的杂志，能看么？</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">做《文周》的前两年，我常常是半宿半宿的扎进稿子里，第二天天一亮，突然就不知道自己到底在干嘛！路上看见报摊，都会绕步走开。不想看别人的杂志，更害怕各种各样的前辈好心指导我怎么做杂志。那种自我怀疑和自我保护意识，让我爬得很慢，却也使得《文周》有了专属于它的气质。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">我希望它和所有杂志都不一样。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">总是在微博上接到私信，“我挨家挨户找了十几家报摊，都说没有你们的杂志，请问到哪可以买到，很想珍藏……”</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">那个时候，我的心便一沉。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">我讨厌自己对着电脑打出的冷冰冰的字：“很抱歉，我们目前只有电子版……”</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">而这样的话，我写了三年。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">在实体刊物衰落的今天，我们依然希望文周能出现在每一个坚持情怀的独立书店，每一个大学图书馆艺术类区域的一角，每一个爱它的人的床头、书柜......</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">我是个急脾气的人，但对于《文周》，我必须等得起。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">柴静的《看见》里说，“许多事情，是有人相信，才会存在。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">”每次《文周》招募志愿者，上百封的申请信里，大都诉说着他们的相信。不光是对《文周》，还有对“精神至上的生活”的相信。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">罗永浩说，不被嘲笑的梦想，是不值得去实现的，这个胖子在保利剧院痞了吧唧的演讲，在某个段落狠狠戳中了我……那一场叫《一个理想主义者的创业故事》。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">但是，我还是想说，在这三年里，我感谢所有真正从心底里相信《文周》和拥有文艺情怀的人，正是你们的“不轻视”，保护了这个襁褓中的婴儿，能够在哆哆嗦嗦的成长中，活到今天，竟然还有了一线希望。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">电影《逆光飞翔》中说，“就是想看看自己能做到多少”。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">有人说：“你不知道，有多少天南海北你不认识的人，在因为《文周》发生着改变”</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">还有人说：“你不做这件事，你就是一个人。你做了，影响的就是10个人、100个人、成千上万的人。地球上几十亿的人，偏偏你被选中做这件事情，何其幸运！”</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">早期的志愿者聚会，AA制。其中有一个骨干，有满满的才华和热情，却总是“有事”不能参加。后来才知道，她是因为交不起那几十元AA的饭钱。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">那姑娘，在无数人为了一张大学录取通知书而挤得头破血流时，却毅然从重点大学不喜欢的专业退学。她只想做跟音乐沾边的事，白天在唱片公司实习，晚上在Live&nbsp;house打工，半夜回到潮湿的租屋里熬夜给《文周》写没有稿费的稿子，日子过得颠沛流离。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">总有人问为什么，她只回答：“快乐啊！”</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">这个志愿者，今天已经是《文周》的执行主编。三年来，没有听过她一声抱怨，每次见她，都是一副阳光幸福的模样。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">还有一个志愿者，做美编，有次连续几夜通宵排版，得了眼疾，一声没吭把活儿干得漂亮，直到发了刊，才去医院治疗。我知道后，哭得厉害，他反到过来笑嘻嘻的安慰我……</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">还有很多《文周》的志愿者，默默付出了一两年，却未谋得一次见面，或许某天在人群中擦身，都认不出这就是和我一起并肩战斗的伙伴。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">......</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">说没想过放弃一定是假的。每当我累极了的时候，团队里总会有人出来说，累了就休息一阵子，有我们呢。是，谁都不会无缘无故这么坚持着，大家每天都活在不留情面的现实生活里，却唯独在这个团队里，包容、忍耐、团结、不计回报的付出。我想，无论遇到什么，只要那个互相拽着的劲儿一直在，这个团队就不会垮，这件事儿就能往下走。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">什么是文艺青年？</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">我喜欢一个读者留言里说的，“与这个时代保持一定距离的人”。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">《文周》100人志愿者团队里的人，年龄身份职业不限，共有的，是身上朴素的气质，始终珍视理想，开放、坦率、自嘲、专注，坚持做一些不断被质疑的事。他们可能永远无法被定义为成功的人，但当他们朝你微笑的时候，你会被他们所传达出的生命力而撞击。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">绿妖说：“北京就是个大精神病院，全国各地有精神病的人早晚都会汇聚到这儿，你看别人都很怪，都有病，你就踏实了。”</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">《文周》三年来采访过的人，大都注重自身专业领域的探索而隔离浮华。他们钻到不被大多数人理解的世界里，与这个有些坏的时代周旋，那其中的苦与乐，是一般人根本无法体会的私享幸福。他们生活在成人和孩子中间的青涩地带，渴望分享、渴望自由。正是这些人，让这个充满了悲观和负面情绪的世界，多了一些让人热泪盈眶的理由和干净的存在。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\">正如一位志愿者写的：“文艺不是一件值得炫耀的事，也不应该遭致诋毁，它是一种平凡的始于爱而止于爱的生活态度，不装腔作势，不随波逐流，心平气和地自省，对逼仄的人生从一而终。”</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 27px; list-style: none; font-f